  "texts": [
    "Such prominence firmly establishes China as a pivotal player in this domain, with its three top prolific authors solidifying its stature.",
    "Regarding RQ2, Fig. 4 illustrates that countries/regions with robust international collaborations tend to exhibit substantial progress and growth in the field, exemplified by the achievements of the USA, the UK, China, and India.",
    "This underscores the significance of global cooperation in propelling the advancement of this emerging domain, facilitating the harnessing of opportunities, and the effective addressing of challenges that may arise.",
    "Figures 5, 6, 7 and 8 also imply that institutions and authors hailing from the same geographical regions are inclined to engage in this multidisciplinary research.",
    "This pattern could stem from the inherent ease of communication and resource sharing within proximity."
  ]
}